GBAtemp has kindly partnered up with Tesla's CEO "Elon Musk" to promote our latest cryptocurrency sca- I-I mean... legit token known as Tempycoin. Are you all excited for this?
If you're a cryptocurrency enthusiast, then you'll sure love Tempycoin. This all-new mint treasured coin can be spent on Patron perks as opposed to XP or any other form of payment, as well as many other amazing opportunities such as an exclusive custom theme to your liking and our dedicated Tempycoin chat room, so you can speak to Tempycoin collectors from around the globe.
Furthermore, we have a special offer for one lucky temper who visits this stream. Anyone who visits the stream in time will have a chance to win a visit to Mr. Beast's house to take part in a $10,000.00 24-hour challenge at random. But wait! There's more. You'll also get to meet your favourite GBAtemp member in real life. YES! You can even get to meet the legendary gamer deluxe himself, p1ngpong.
The stream has already gone live, so what are you waiting for? Hurry so that you don't miss out on what we have to offer.
